					A woman sells fresh fish at a market in Quy Nhon, Vietnam (Pascal Deloche/Godong/Universal Images Group via Getty Images)
				</div>
					</div>

		<div class="clearfix">
			<div class="txt-center pv-md">
				<span class="txt-muted">
					Published 27 Jul 2022&nbsp;
				</span>

