        <i class="icon icon-social-linkedin"></i>
      </a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a class="txt-dn" href="mailto:?subject=What+Vietnam+can+learn+from+Thailand%E2%80%99s+fight+against+illegal+fishing&amp;body=https://www.lowyinstitute.org/the-interpreter/what-vietnam-can-learn-thailand-s-fight-against-illegal-fishing">
